OOC: All right, a reintro of Waspinator

He had been forgotten when the Pred and Maximals had left, left on 
earth to be worshiped by fleshybots but that grown tiresome, and 
Waspinator longed to be back in battle. His luck had been with him for 
the Maximals and Predacons had returned in a mass of glory and the Pred 
had been estatic, returning to his rightful place next to Megatron.

Now that Megatron had become Hydras, the bug bot had still stayed at 
his side, even if he did change and maybe become a bit meaner. But he 
would still be a faithful Predacon. The large metal wasp buzzed about 
the base, dropping to land on a nearby crate of some bots. "Wazzpinator 
help," the bug bot buzzed. "Wazzpinator help other botzz  build." 
Wasipinator gave a flutter of his wings. "Wazzipinator do good, not be 
blown up."

OOC: This was a post that was directed to some bots that were deciding 
to build a weapon... I can't remember who they were sorry. Maybe 
someone could just stumble upon our little bot that would be good too 
lol

OMWOS
